Sentencas: NiO/samaria doped ceria (NiO/SDC) anodes with gradient Ni composition distribution were prepared by a process based on tape casting and laminating.
Titulo: Gradient Ni/SDC anodes for solid oxide fuel cells by tape casting

Sentencas: Sintering behaviors, microstructure and thermal properties of the gradient anodes were investigated, and compared with those of two NiO/SDC anodes with single NiO composition (75 and 55% NiO).
Titulo: Gradient Ni/SDC anodes for solid oxide fuel cells by tape casting

Sentencas: It was shown that the gradient NiO/SDC anode has fine pore and grain structure and steady thermal expansion coefficients (TEC) than each anode with homogeneous Ni composition distribution.
Titulo: Gradient Ni/SDC anodes for solid oxide fuel cells by tape casting

Sentencas: Owing to the better microstructure and properties, SOFCs based on the gradient anode with a SDC electrolyte film of about 100 mum in thickness and a LSCF cathode showed a maximum power density of 80 MW/cm(2) at 600degreesC.
Titulo: Gradient Ni/SDC anodes for solid oxide fuel cells by tape casting
